oadSuccess && cursor != null\n          ? (state as MatchListLoadSuccess).matche
s\n          : <Map<String, dynamic>>[];\n      emit(MatchListLoadSuccess(\n    
   matches: [...currentMatches, ...items],\n        hasMore: result[\'has_more\'
] as bool? ?? false,\n        nextCursor: result[\'next_cursor\'] as String?,\n 
    ));\n    } on Exception catch (e) {\n      emit(MatchListLoadFailure(e.toStr
ing()));\n    }\n  }\n  ```\n- **依据**: PRD `v1-matching.md` 第 192-195 行要求
游标分页；当前实现不符合分页追加预期。\n\n### 6. 后端单元测试覆盖不足\n- **位置*
